Date:  0/0/1937
Source:  Dictionary of Slang
Author:  PARTRIDGE
Vol / Page:  307
Edition:
Quote:  Fuller's earth. New Zealand: theatrical and cinematic: from ca. 1912. Punning on the Fuller brothers, who, ca. 1910-30, owned a great number of N.Z. theatres and cinemas. (The Daily Telegraph, July 23, 1934.)
